# Beaconchain Dashboard

[![Build](https://github.com/beaconchain-com/beaconcha.in/actions/workflows/build.yaml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/beaconchain-com/beaconcha.in/actions/workflows/build.yaml)

**Beaconchain Dashboard** is an open-source Ethereum 2.0 validator performance tracker app for Android and iOS. It uses the [beaconcha.in API](https://beaconcha.in/api/v1/docs/).

[![Get it on Google Play](https://beaconcha.in/img/android.png)](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=in.beaconcha.mobile)
[![Get it on App Store](https://beaconcha.in/img/ios.png)](https://apps.apple.com/at/app/beaconchain-dashboard/id1541822121)

---

## About

This app is built with **Angular** (TypeScript, HTML, CSS) and **Ionic Framework** for mobile UI components. **Ionic Capacitor** serves as the bridge for native code.

## Features

- Track your validators' online status, balance, returns, and more  
- Receive various notification alerts for your validators  
- Combined dashboard view  
- Support for up to 100 validators  
- Ethereum client update notifications  
- Network warnings  
- Multiple currencies support  
- Mainnet & Testnet support  
- Add validators via public key, index, or ETH1 deposit address  
- Light & Dark theme

## Device Support

- Android 5.0 or newer  
- iOS 11 or newer

